import { formatCountry } from '../utils/formatCountry'; import { formatDate } from '../utils/formatDate'; import './content.css'; interface IContent { data: any; } export function Content({data}: IContent) { // console.log('content: ', data) return (

{data.name} {formatCountry(data.sys.country)}

{formatDate(new Date()).month + ' ' + formatDate(new Date()).date + ', ' + formatDate(new Date()).year} {formatDate(new Date()).day}
  • Temperature: {data.main.temp} C
  • Feels like: {data.main.feels_like} C
  • Wind speed: {data.wind.speed} C
  • Humidity: {data.main.humidity} C
) }
